  "title": "Mildly Spicy Saudi Arabian Fish Skewers",
  "description": "A briny and crumbly pescatarian-friendly dish featuring jalapeno, perfect for a energizing meal, this Saudi Arabian fish skewer recipe combines the flavors of the Middle East with a spicy kick.",
