  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Thread the fish fillets, jalapeno peppers, and garlic onto the wooden skewers.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the lemon juice, olive oil, salt, black pepper, paprika, and zaatar.",
    "Brush the mixture onto the fish and jalapeno peppers.",
    "Grill the skewers for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally, until the fish is cooked through.",
    "Serve the skewers hot, garnished with additional jalapeno slices and lemon wedges if desired."
